od resources, for frugivorous bats with different foraging requirements in coffee plantations, will benefit the resilience of bats to modification of their natural habitat.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Salda\u00f1a-V\u00e1zquez, Romeo A.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Sosa, Vinicio J.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Hern\u00e1ndez-Montero, Jes\u00fas R.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "L\u00f3pez-Barrera, Fabiola", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/ccb85ac9ddac2f7616fe81c352a60f7e", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/53c3b9296cc0301c537f28ac3ab869dd46cfc59cce3a05bc873f249cb68f473e", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/IK9DFUTZ", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/IK9DFUTZ", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/eb94ed86ce4dbd70b9ffc5bdbed08d46!/b105471-108061", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/330417efcaa2560c9b8ebcd6fae17ce0", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"issue": "7", "pages": "2111-2124", "title": "Biodiversity and Conservation", "volume": "19"}, "alternate_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/ccb85ac9ddac2f7616fe81c352a60f7e"}, {"identifier": "urn:lsid:zotero.org:groups:5435545:items:IK9DFUTZ"}, {"identifier": "10.1007/s10531-010-9829-6"}], "communities": [{"id": "batlit"}, {"id